# Codebase-audit

- Evidence-tiers: `docs/CODEBASE_AUDIT_EVIDENCE.md`
- Snelle smoke: `windows/audits/RUN_CODEBASE_SMOKE_AUDIT.bat` (conda `hermes-env`)
- Geen "release-ready" zonder E3 (`RUN_PYTEST.ps1` / `RUN_AUDITS -IncludeAllE2E`)
- Optioneel na pull/update: `-IncludeCodebaseSmoke` (~32s) of `-IncludeCodebaseSmokeE2E` (~45s); helper `windows/scripts/Invoke-PostSyncCodebaseSmoke.ps1` (standaard uit)
